Package Messages

Class Summary
AlterLogin This class is intended to ask the server to alter a login credential in some way.
AlterPhase This class is intended to ask the server to alter the current phase.
GetInfo The class is a general purpose request statement for miscellaneous use throughout this program.
InfoMessage This class may to be used to send many types of miscellaneous types of information throughout this project.
LeaderboardUpdate This class is used to update the clients as to the status of the leaderboard.
LoginAttempt This class facilitates login attempts by both admin users and teams.
LoginStatus This class is a response from the server after receiving a LoginAttempt.
WithdrawSubmission This class is a request from a team to withdraw a pending or running submission.
